Implementation Specification - Volume 4

AWX / Ansible Tower Design

Version: 1.0

Status: Approved Baseline

---

1. Purpose

This document defines:

- AWX Organization Structure
- Inventories
- Credentials
- Job Templates
- Workflow Templates
- Surveys
- Runtime Host Injection
- Notification Integration
- RBAC Model

This specification shall be treated as the source of truth for AWX implementation.

---

2. AWX Architecture

The framework shall use AWX for:

Workflow Orchestration
Job Execution
Credential Management
Notifications
Execution History
Artifact Publication

AWX shall NOT be used for:

Configuration Storage
Checkpoint Storage
Report Storage
Manifest Storage

These remain in source control or runtime filesystem.

---

3. AWX Organization Structure

Recommended:

Organization

└── Regression Automation

All framework artifacts belong to this organization.

---

4. AWX Project Structure

Project Name:

Regression Automation Framework

Repository:

regression-automation-framework

Update Strategy:

Update Revision On Launch = Enabled

---

5. Inventory Strategy

IMPORTANT

Static inventories shall NOT contain runtime execution hosts.

Reason:

Host selected at runtime

Inventory should contain only framework execution metadata.

Example:

Framework Inventory

└── localhost

---

6. Runtime Host Injection Strategy

Host supplied by survey:

Example:

targetHost=qa-host01

Workflow performs:

add_host:
  name: "{{ targetHost }}"
  groups: runtime_execution

Subsequent plays execute against:

runtime_execution

No permanent inventory updates allowed.

---

7. AWX Credentials

Required Credentials:

Machine Credential
Artifactory Credential
SMTP Credential (optional)
Vault Credential (future)

---

8. Machine Credential

Purpose:

SSH access to runtime host

Fields:

Username
SSH Private Key
Privilege Escalation Password (optional)

---

9. Artifactory Credential

Purpose:

Artifact download authentication

Fields:

Username
Password
Token

Must be injected as environment variables.

---

10. Credential Rules

Credentials SHALL:

Never be stored in Git

Never be stored in group_vars

Never be stored in manifests

Never be written to reports

---

11. Survey Architecture

All executions shall be launched through surveys.

---

12. Survey Fields

Required Fields:

Environment
Target Host
Manifest Path
Execution Mode

---

13. Environment Survey Field

Type:

Multiple Choice

Allowed Values:

DEV
QA
UAT
PROD

Required:

YES

---

14. Target Host Survey Field

Type:

Text

Example:

qa-regression-host01

Required:

YES

---

15. Manifest Path Survey Field

Type:

Text

Example:

manifests/run_001.json

Required:

YES

---

16. Execution Mode Survey Field

Allowed Values:

PARALLEL
SEQUENTIAL
RESUME

Required:

YES

---

